The Department of Justice has unsealed charges against an individual connected to Iran's Islamic Revolutionary Guard Corps. The charges relate to Iran's alleged attempts to carry out an assassination against former National Security Advisor John Bolton in the United States. The Biden Administration emphasizes its commitment to protecting Americans against violence and terrorism, stating that Iran will face severe consequences if it attacks any U.S. citizens. The government will utilize all available resources to ensure the safety of Americans. The Department of Justice and the Federal Bureau of Investigation are praised for their efforts in this case.